sentences.english: If all the IZs in the province were filled up, environment pollution would be a great deal more serious.
sentences.chinese: 如果省內的工業區全部投產，環境污染將更加嚴重。

sentences.english: The field could enter production as soon as 2012.
sentences.chinese: 這座油田可能在2012年就能投產。

sentences.english: The long-distance natural gas transmission pipe of Shanxi province was operated in the 1997.
sentences.chinese: 陝西省天然氣長輸管道於1997年投產。

sentences.english: The popular Toyota Prius, for example, is not yet manufactured in the United States.
sentences.chinese: 例如，熱銷的豐田普拉斯還未在美國投產。

sentences.english: The launch of their new machines in this factory received much media coverage.
sentences.chinese: 這個工廠投產的新機器廣獲傳媒報道。

sentences.english: Microsoft's senior executives certainly hope that Rashid's latest crop of researchers come up with the goods.
sentences.chinese: 微軟的高層很希望拉希德最新的研究成果投產。

sentences.english: The operation actualities of Mahuining oil pipeline is introduced.
sentences.chinese: 介紹了馬惠寧輸油管道的施工和投產後的運行現狀。

sentences.english: The technology of well completion and putting into production for gas wells with high sulfur content is not available in China.
sentences.chinese: 高酸性氣井完井投產在國內是空白，屬一項新工藝。

sentences.english: The first CRVS will be production-ready in early 2010.
sentences.chinese: 第一套CRVS系統將在2010年初投產。

sentences.english: The Anhui-province plant, west of Shanghai, is slated to go online next year.
sentences.chinese: 該工廠位於安徽，計劃明年建成投產。

sentences.english: Transition of launch programs into volume production.
sentences.chinese: 將投產項目轉化成量產。

sentences.english: To be operated by SAC, the facility will be completed by the end of the year and will start production next year.
sentences.chinese: 由沈飛來運作，工廠將在年底完成，明年投產。

sentences.english: Mr. Chang estimated that it could be a decade before China’s stealth plane enters production.
sentences.chinese: 平先生估計，中國的隱形飛機投產可能還需十年時間。

sentences.english: In 2000, our Dongguan plant went into operation. The business expanded rapidly with products selling worldwide.
sentences.chinese: 2000年，公司在東莞廠投產，迅速取得經營規模。

sentences.english: It will definitely be produced in HVF.
sentences.chinese: 這裏將肯定會在這裏投產。

sentences.english: AISC new No3 sintering workiship since its commissioning has not reached the design capacity for many-years.
sentences.chinese: 鞍鋼新三燒投產多年，一直沒有達產。
